Malice:  
 
He walked toward the coordinates given to him by Rodimus, quiet for a bit, sorting his thoughts.  On one hand he had deeply hurt himself and Blacknightmare, but on the other he could live freely with his first true love, Wolfblade.  After a while he smiled, and paused in his stride.  he held out his hand to Wolfblade, a smile so true and reflecting how he felt.
 
Free, his spark no longer under the burden it was, free to love Wolfblade and keep his promise to Blacknightmare and Hellplague.

Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@...> wrote:
WOlfblade::

She dared not say a word. He looked like the pit. She nodded her head
to him and followed him.


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
